**Contains:** - System Property "adobe.dc.pdf.embed.api.key" - Widget "[AAG] Adobe Embed API Reader" - Widget "[AAG] Adobe Embed API Metadata" - Test page "[AAG] Adobe Embed API - Test Page" *************** Test in /sp as it needs a js that is included in the theme used by default in /sp - JS Include: "https://documentcloud.adobe.com/view-sdk/main.js" included to theme "La Jolla" (by default in /sp) - Attachment (PDF file)
**Test:** https:<instance-name>.service-now.com/sp?id=_aag_adobe_embed_api&sysparm_domain_restore=false&sysparm_stack=no
**Info:** - Adobe credential is associated to domain "service-now.com" thus the test would only work on PDI instances. For sales-dev, we do need to create a new crendentials. - How to create credentials (for free): https://www.adobe.io/apis/documentcloud/dcsdk/gettingstarted.html - API documentation & Analytics collected: https://www.adobe.io/apis/documentcloud/dcsdk/docs.html - Sample repo: https://github.com/adobe/pdf-embed-api-samples
